Section: oldlibs
Architecture: all
Depends: lynx-cur (>= ${source:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Wrapper for lynx-cur (transitional package)
 This is a transitional package and can safely be removed; see the
 lynx-cur package instead.

